				<wikidot:authorName>hungrypossum</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5682709</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Patheticon the Garglemost and Pesterbot</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>Observations are made via an opaque glass window to prevent SCP-1370 from attacking its own reflection.</p> </blockquote> <p>I'd upvote this several times over, it's brilliant</p> 
				 	]]>
