					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-467829#post-4470821</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-467829/scp-1370#post-4470821</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2020 20:26:03 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Bob the Inept</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3395949</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It looks like it is not just anomalously animated, but fails without fail anomalously. I prefer it the way it is written, where this aspect is not mentioned (if indeed it was meant to be this way). Writing it out would kill the joke.</p> <p>I almost no-voted because I've already seen similar things like the Lunatic (I know it's actually a potent thing) and the abysmal typewriter. But this is so gosh darn well executed I couldn't not upvote the quality.</p> <p>Also, I have a feeling that the people who say this and other funny articles should be -J actually haven't read any -J articles.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
