					<![CDATA[
						 <p>If I may, this SCP is more dangerous than we may think, because the photo taken by SCP-978 shows a mass of pipes, clockworks, and gears appear while SCP-1370 is no where to be seen.<br /> It also threatens destruction all around it but is unable to do anything. How are we sure that SCP-1370 is not the mind of the broken god put in a weaker body, because the recent SCP-001 proposal depicts a somewhat similar entity.</p> 
