						 <p>Plus all of the ones.</p> <p>The laughter built so. It did. It had me snickering, then giggling, then chuckling, then haw-hawing.</p> <p>And then this bomb dropped:</p> <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-1370:</strong> <em>(approaching the plant)</em> Who dares. All souls will burn. You will feel the sharp sting of my wrath. Identify yourself so that I may sing damnation upon you as you die.</p> <p><strong>P. Davies:</strong> I am a split-leaf philodendron, a semi-woody shrub with large glossy leaves. <em>(restrained laughter)</em> These leaves can grow up to three feet long.</p> </blockquote> <p>I lost all sense of reason and self control at that point.</p> 
				 	]]>
